INUMBER 1551
NAME 1442
MISC
WEIGHT 2
VOLUME 2
*DESCRIPTION_START READ
                       THE CRYSTAL HORN

     My researches have shown that the Crystal Horn was created by Shemri
to call forth the Pegasi from the Silver Pools where they were born. The
Horn has long been lost. Rumors speak of it being scattered in four pieces.
Hidden in four different locations to keep it safe, until such time as a
brave person, or persons, will take the risk to find it. I have found the
mouthpiece of the Horn, and now entrust it to whomever comes across this
parchment. Before I left Fayd, so many years ago now, I placed the location
where the Quest for the four seperate pieces of the Horn can begin, in the
mind of an old priest of Shemri. His name escapes me now, but, with gentle
prodding, the information will be forthcoming.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
