INUMBER 1705
NAME 384
MISC
WEIGHT 3
VOLUME 2
ARTICLE THE
OPENABLE
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
Beautiful hand-tooled leather shines with a deep, polished lustre. Intricate
designs of vibrant oak trees flow across the cover of the book, the branches
of the trees enveloping the gilden lettering that announces the title of the
book as, "The Book of Tales"
*DESCRIPTION_END
VARIABLE tales
IFVERB OPEN -1
  CLEARVERB
  IFVAR tales = 0
   ADD tales 1
    IFVAR tales = 1
     ECHO PLAYER You open the cover of the book slowly, exposing beautifully aged pages with colorful script flowing over them. Golden dust, sparkling in the light, flows from the book and covers your listeners.
     ECHO OTHERS %N opens the beautifully worked book, running %h hands over the hand-tooled leather. A golden dust, sparkling in the light, flows from the book and covers you, entrancing you and opening your mind to the wonders of the story that lies ahead...
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFPREVERB PUSH -1
  CLEARVERB
  ADD tales 1
   IFVAR tales = 2
     ECHO PLAYER You lean back for a moment, closing your eyes and letting the flow of words embed themselves in your mind, with a smile you open your eyes and lean forward, the words beginning to flow from your mouth...
     ECHO OTHERS %N leans back for a moment, closing %h eyes, then %s leans forward a smile gracing %h face as the wondrous story begins to flow from %h lips...
   ENDIF
    IFVAR tales = 3
     ECHO PLAYER Your words, strong and vibrant, echo around the area, animating the golden dust that still sparkles in the air, causing it to animate and play out the scenes from your tale...
     ECHO OTHERS %N's words, strong and vibrant, echo beautifully around the area, animating the golden dust that still sparkles in the air. Glancing at the dust you see it animate and begin to play out the scenes from %N's tale...
    ENDIF
     IFVAR tales = 4
      ECHO PLAYER You lean forward, calling down shimmering motes of starlight with your words, the motes dance around the golden dust, interacting with it in a complex pattern of beauty.
      ECHO OTHERS %N leans forward, %h entrancing words calling down shimmering motes of starlight from the sky, the motes descend gently and dance around the golden dust, interacting with it in a complex pattern of beauty, their movements controlled by %N's voice...
     ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB CLOSE -1
  CLEARVERB
   IFVAR tales => 1
     ECHO PLAYER Your last words hang on the air, their magic still entrancing your audience with the beauty of your tale, as you lean back and close the book.
     ECHO OTHERS %N leans back and closes the book, %h last words still hanging in the air, slowly fading, the magic of the tale still entrancing you with wonder...
     EQUAL tales 0
   ENDIF
   IFVAR tales = 0
     ECHO PLAYER The book is already closed.
   ENDIF
ENDIF
