NUMBER 3862
NAME Black Tower, catwalk
ASTRAL
OBSCURED_DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
A black stone catwalk extends from the black tower towards a large tree to
east. The catwalk runs straight through the rustling treetops making it hard
to discern anything beyond your immediate surroundings. Directly to the north
,though, is a gap in the trees that allows an unobstructed view of the
catwalk leading from the white tower. The white tower catwalk is too far away
to reach from this point, but you think that you can see the vague outline of
a figure standing upon it. A few feet from the black marble arch
that leads back into the black tower is what you take to be a statue...
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 3863
ITEM 0 60 ADJ1=25 ADJ2=187 VAL2=3861
ITEM 1 346
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
As you study the statue closer you realize that it is not a statue at all,
a living person! Dressed in swirling black robes the figure looks exactly
like the painting in the living chamber below. The figures' hands are raised
in a warding gesture, as if caught in the midst of preparing a spell. A
strange blue field crackles slowly around the figure.
*DESCRIPTION_END
MONSTER_GROUP 118
IFPREVERB THUMP 1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER Your fist bounces off the field.
  ECHO OTHERS %N's fist bounces off the strange blue field.
ENDIF
IFPREVERB LEAN 1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The blue field repels you, causing you to fall down!
  ECHO OTHERS The blue field repels %N, causing %i to fall down!
  POSITION LAY
ENDIF
IFPREVERB BREAK 1
  CLEARVERB
  ECHO PLAYER The blue field lashes out at you!
  DAMAGE BODYONLY 25 %N screams in pain as the blue field lashes out at %i!
ENDIF
IFVERB RECALL -1
  IFVAR SKILL23 => 25
    ECHO PLAYER The strange blue field surrounding the 'statue' is a complex form of time magic. The figure inside is caught inside this field and is moving at an incredibly slow rate of speed compared to the rest of the world. Even the simple act of raising his hand would take the figure nearly a hundred years.
  ENDIF
ENDIF
;
