NUMBER 28
NAME Hill of Heroes
OUTDOOR_FLOOR
DAY_LIGHT
*DESCRIPTION_START
Gleaming gold braziers line the gravel path that passes by beautifully
worked statues of purest white marble. The eternally burning fires in
the braziers illuminate the dazzling works of art with their magical
light, accentuating the beautiful work put into the statues. A gentle
breeze from the grasslands flows across the ground, causing the stalks
of emerald green grass dotting the hilltop to flutter gently. Comfortable
marble benches line the gravel path, set in positions that enhance the
gorgeous view.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT S 2599
ITEM 0 339 ADJ1=187
ITEM 1 346 ADJ1=347 ADJ2=187
EXTEND 1 of a Highlander
ITEM 2 346 ADJ1=347 ADJ2=187
EXTEND 2 of three beings
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 1
An intricate sculpture of a handome highlander warrior meets your gaze.
The strong warrior has his hands clenched firmly around the hilt of a
shimmering sword. Below him, prone, is the form of Siryx, the Usurper.
The highlander has been captured, for eternity, as he is bringing the
sword down upon Siryx. Siryx has his hands raised, as if to ward off
the blow, and a look of terror is obvious upon his face. There is an
inscription at the base of the statue.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 1
        Korazon Mountainmover
      Champion of Amilor and the
   bane of Siryx. Wielding the mighty
    blade named Godslayer he did put
      an end to the Usurper's plans
         in the year 1023.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAMINE 2
In the foreground of the statue stand three beings, a human female and
two ephemerals, male and female. Behind them, not detracting from them
in any way, stands a majestic crystal dragon, its wings outstretched
to encompass the figures in the foreground. The human female, dazzling
in her beauty and strength, holds a wooden staff of deeply magical power.
The ephemerals, their sculptures reflecting conviction, power and beauty,
have their hands clasped near their chests, where the Heartstone pulsates
in both of them. There is an inscription at the base of the statue.
*DESCRIPTION_END
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM READ 2
      Aeyria Hiehthu, Ria Sheehe and Vastenio Solaris.
     The Chosen One and the bearers of the Heartstone
     The Song's call did they answer, to stop a plague
      and to bring the guardians back. Their powers
       joined together to accomplish these greatest
             of deeds in the year 1027.
*DESCRIPTION_END
;
INUMBER 800
NAME 318
ARMOR
WORN_DON
WEIGHT 1
VOLUME 1
*DESCRIPTION_START EXAMINE
Lines of shimmering magic flow around the Dragon flight, highlighting
each dragon with its own unique color.
*DESCRIPTION_END
IFPREVERB RUB -1
  CLEARVERB
  ADD FLAG4 1
   IFVAR FLAG4 = 1
     ECHO PLAYER You feel your mind flowing into the center of the pin, stars and the blackness of space pass by you in the twinkling of an eye, and then you see yourself flying through the stars alongside the flight of Dragons...
     ECHO OTHERS For the briefest of moments you see the form of a majestic crystal Dragon outlined over the form of %N.
     PLREVENT 1
     CONTPLREVENT
     ECHO PLAYER The power and majesty of Dragonkind flows through your body as you fly through the stars, each star brightening as you pass by it. The journey reaches its end and you find yourself hovering before a dazzling star of white light at the very center of the universe.
     PLREVENT 1
     CONTPLREVENT
     ECHO PLAYER The melodic, awe-inspiring strains of the Song of the Universe fill your body and soul. As the music passes through you, the final note fading into the vastness of space, you heard a gentle, yet powerful, voice speak in your mind, "Thank you, %N." As the voice fades you feel your mind flow back.
     EQUAL FLAG4 0
   ENDIF
ENDIF
;
