SCRIPTMACRO 86
*DESCRIPTION_START
Standing nearly eight feet tall and with a weight ranging near to that of
a full grown giant this horrid monstrosity created in the infernal pits
of the Brotherhood inspires fear in all who gaze upon it. Made from the
collected body parts of those whom the Brotherhood has collected for
slavery the Zharkier has been given life by foul magic. Each individual
part that makes up the creature has had the skin flayed from it, leaving
only the bloody organ or muscle itself to pulse evilly in the light. A
putrescent, sickly liquid forms a protective coating around the organs
and also drips continously from the creature, creating small piles of
a foul-smelling pus wherever it walks. A sinewy spinal column, glowing
with fiery red nerve endings serves as the creatures tail, while a gaping
hole in the creature's throat emits glowing pustules of blood as the
monster roars.
*DESCRIPTION_END
