TEXX %s removes a flaming, bloody organ and hurls it at %s!
TEXE The stench of infernal pits fills the area.
TEXI The weapon is absorbed by a soft area of bloody tissue.
TEXQ A Zharkier's spinal tail slams the ground in anger.
TEXZ A Zharkier rips %'s flesh away and licks the blood!
TEX1 Blood flows in airy bubbles from a Zharkier.
TEX2 A Zharkier claws the air in berserk fury.
TEXD crumples, blood flowing in pools from its body.
TEXM Leaving behind pools of pus a Zharkier moves
TEXS A Zharkier removes a glowing blood bubble from its throat.
TEXL A Zharkier throws the glowing blood bubble
TEXA Claws dripping sickly ichor a Zharkier leaps
